## ğŸ¨ Tailwind Setup Notes
- Tailwind config file: `tailwind.config.js`
- Output CSS must be generated with PostCSS or Vite plugin.
- If you're using Vite:
```bash
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init
```
Then include this in `tailwind.config.js`:
```js
content: ["./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}"]
```

And add Tailwind to your CSS entry file:
```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

